data.description: Location, Location, Location!!! Just blocks to Asante Hospital and Rogue Valley country club, this gem ofa home has lots to offer. Big back yard, mature trees, quite street to live on but with access to medical,shopping, and much more. This beautifully well kept home has living room with fire place, family roomwith fireplace and slider leading to deck and back yard, it has a well-appointed kitchen which overlooksthe private back yard, real hard wood floors and 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths. Do not miss youropportunity to own this nice home and all it has to offer. Move in ready and waiting for you and yourfamily.Call today for your personal tour.
